industrialized country and their leaders that have great impacts
on the club on the matter of Russia's club membership.
</P>
<P>
Russia itself is a large creditor nation inheriting 190 billion
U.S. dollars from the former Soviet Union, he said, and would get
back quite a big portion of the money.
</P>
<P>
He made it clear that Russia will only pay back loans which
have specific date of repayment. enditem
