the day as it rose by 20 cents to finish at 23.2 Singapore
dollars. The Development Bank of Singapore (DBS) Foreign, food and
soft drinks maker F&AMP;N, and the Singapore Airlines (SIA) Foreign
increased by ten cents each to end at 15.8, 9.1 and 12.7 Singapore
dollars respectively.
