loser as it declined by 1.8 dollars to close at 7.2 dollars. Ber
Land fell by 1.61 dollars to finish at 1.24 dollars. The Overseas
Chinese Banking Corporation (OCBC) Foreign ended 40 cents lower at
10.7 Singapore dollars.  
