<HEADLINE> Editorial Hails Successful Conclusion of 15th Party Congress (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The newly elected Central Committee includes a number of
long-tested senior officials, some middle-aged officials grown up
since the founding of new China and some young officials who have
both ability and political integrity, the editorial noted.
</P>
<P>
This shows that the Party's cause is flourishing and does not
lack successors, it said.
</P>
<P>
"The primary task of the whole party is to study and implement
the guidelines of the Party Congress, unify our thinking and
strive for the grand goal set forth by the Party congress," the
editorial said.
</P>
<P>
The most important aspect in implementing the guidelines of the
Party Congress is to arm the whole Party, leading officials and
people in the country with Deng Xiaoping Theory, it said.
</P>
<P>
Deng Xiaoping Theory is the heritage and development of Mao
Zedong Thought and Marxism in modern China, and it is the powerful
spiritual support in invigorating the Chinese nation, it said,
adding that history has proved and will continue to prove that
only Deng Xiaoping Theory which combines Marxism with China's
actual conditions and the characteristics of the times can
correctly solve the future and destiny of socialism in China.
</P>
<P>
The principle of emancipating the mind and seeking truth from
facts is "the quintessence of Deng Xiaoping Theory, the cherished
heritage of the Chinese communists and the everlasting truth of
Maxism," it said.
</P>
<P>
The whole Party should implement the principle and start from
the actual situation that China is still in the primary stage of
socialism, continue the reforms and open up wider to the outside
world and promote the national economy to develop in a fast,
sustainable and healthy manner and achieve the all-round social
progress, the editorial stressed.
</P>
