<HEADLINE> Armenian Communist Party Congratulates CPC on Congress </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 18 (Xinhua) -- The Armenian Communist Party
has sent a congratulatory message to the Communist Party of China
(CPC) on its 15th National Congress, which opened here last Friday.
</P>
<P>
The congress surely will carry on courageously the great cause
of building socialism with Chinese characteristics initiated by
Deng Xiaoping, said S. Badalyan, first secretary of the party, in
the message.
</P>
<P>
Through collective wisdom, CPC is surely able to resolve every
complex problem to meet the challenges of the times, he believed.
</P>
