<HEADLINE> Party Congress Approves Report by 14th CPC Central Committee </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 18 (Xinhua) -- The 15th Communist Party of
China (CPC) Central Committee approved today the keynote report by
Jiang Zemin on behalf of the 14th CPC Central Committee at the
opening session on September 12.
</P>
<P>
The resolution adopted by the Congress today says that the
report has summed up history and made plans for the future. It has
planned, in an all-round way, the trans-century development in
China's reform and opening up as well as modernization drive. It
is a political manifestation and platform for action of the Party
to lead people of all nationalities to the new century, says the
resolution.
</P>
<P>
It accords with the demands of the times and is in keeping with
the aspiration of the people for the report to affirm the theme of
holding high the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory to advance,
in an all-round manner, the great cause of building socialism with
Chinese characteristics to the next century, it says.
</P>
<P>
The congress urged the whole Party never to waver in holding
high the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory to concentrate on
the central task of economic construction by seizing the
opportunity and forging ahead in a pioneering manner to work for
new breakthroughs in economic restructuring, the resolution says.
</P>
<P>
The congress also urged continued effort to deepen the reform
of political structure, and enhanced work in achieving cultural
and ethical progress with concerted efforts by different walks of
life to achieve all-round progress in economic development and
social advances.
</P>
<P>
Highly appraising the work by the 14th CPC Central Committee,
the resolution says, the Congress held that the 14th Central
Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin as the core made great
achievements by leading the Chinese Communist Party and the people
in continuing the march along the road of building socialism with
Chinese characteristics and pushing to a new stage reform,
opening-up and socialist modernization drive. The policy decisions
of the 14th National Congress were correct, it states, and our
Party proved its ability of managing the situation in complicated
domestic and international circumstances.
</P>
<P>
The congress unanimously agreed to adopt Deng Xiaoping Theory
as the guiding ideology of the Party and to clearly write it down
in the Party Constitution, the resolution says. The whole Party
should conscientiously apply Deng Xiaoping Theory as the guide to
our cause and continue to enrich and develop it in the course of
practice, it says.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
