<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970918.0170 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-18 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Party Congress Approves Report by 14th CPC Central Committee (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The congress was of the view that Jiang's report further
emphasized the thesis that China is in a primary stage of
socialism, the resolution says, adding that this is of utmost
importance. The congress endorsed the Party's basic programs in
the primary stage of socialism as laid down in the report, it
says. The whole Party should unswervingly adhere to the Party's
basic line and implement the basic programs in an all-round
manner.
</P>
<P>
The congress approved the arrangements for the reform and
development in China's economic, political and cultural fields, it
says. It says the period from now on to the first ten years of the
next century is a crucial period in China's socialist
modernization.
</P>
<P>
During the period, it says, China must actively promote the
fundamental shifts in economic structure and the mode of economic
growth so as to build a more complete socialist market economic
structure and maintain a rapid, steady and healthy economic
development,with an objective of laying a solid foundation for
realizing basic modernization by the middle of the next century,
the resolution says.
</P>
<P>
China must promote political restructuring on the condition of
adhering to the four cardinal principles, further expand socialist
democracy, improve the socialist legal system, manage the state
according to law, so as to build a socialist country ruled by law,
the resolution says.
</P>
<P>
The resolution also urges the country to enhance the ethical
progress and place priority in development strategy of science and
technology as well as education and actively promote the
development of various social causes.
</P>
<P>
It is the basic guarantee of national security and
modernization to strengthen national defense and army building,
the resolution says, after approving the arrangement in report on
national defense and army building.
</P>
<P>
The congress expressed China's determination to realize the
complete, ultimate reunification of the motherland under the
concept of "one country, two systems".
</P>
<P>
On international situation and foreign policy, the resolution
says China will unswervingly follow an independent foreign policy,
oppose hegemonism, safeguard world peace to promote advances of
humankind.
</P>
<P>
The key to fulfilling the strategic goals and various tasks set
forth in the report is to adhere to strengthening and improving
the leadership of the Party, the resolution says.
</P>
<P>
To promote the great cause of Party building, the CPC must
strengthen the Party's construction in ideology, organization and
style of work.
</P>
<P>
The resolution also urges strict management of the Party
affairs. Efforts must be made to unswervingly continue its
anti-corruption struggle.
</P>
<P>
The congress called on all the Party membership to hold high
the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory and rally around the CPC
Central Committee to lead people of all nationalities to advance
the great cause of building socialism with Chinese characteristics
to the 21st century. 
</P>
</TEXT>
