Maria-Alejandra Vento of Venezuela 7-5, 6-2 to snatch her first
quarter-final berth Thursday in the 450,000 U.S. dollars Princess
Cup tennis tournament.
</P>
<P>
Li lost her first game on a close line call, broke back in the
next game and never trailed again in the 90-minute match wherein
Vento made a series of unforced errors.
</P>
