Arantxa Sanchez Vicario of Spain or Japan's Shinobu Asagoe.
</P>
<P>
In another rain-interrupted second-round match, American fourth
seed Kimberly Po came from behind to beat French Open mixed
doubles champion Rika Hiraki of Japan 3-6, 7-6 (8/6), 6-3. 
</P>
