<DOCNO> XIE19970918.0192 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-18 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> 15th National Party Congress Closes (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The congress urged the whole Party to unswerving hold high the
great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory to concentrate on the central
task of economic development by seizing the opportunity and
forging ahead in a pioneering manner to work for new breakthroughs
in economic restructuring.
</P>
<P>
The congress also called for continued efforts for the reform
of political structure, strengthened work in achieving cultural
and ethical progress with concerted efforts by people from the
different walks of life to achieve all-round progress in economic
development and social advances.
</P>
<P>
Today's session also passed a resolution on the amendment to
the Constitution of the Communist Party of China, which took
effect as soon as the amendment resolution was passed.
</P>
<P>
The congress held that it is of great and far-reaching
significance to establish Deng Xiaoping Theory as the guiding
ideology of the Party in the Party Constitution and take Marxism,
Leninism, Mao Zedong Thought and Deng Xiaoping Theory as the
Party's guide for action.
</P>
<P>
The move will guarantee that the Communist Party of China will
lead the people in building a prosperous, democratic, civilized,
socialist modern country by firmly adhering to the road of
socialism with Chinese characteristics.
</P>
<P>
The congress also passed a resolution on the work report of the
Central Commission for Discipline Inspection, fully approved the
work of the commission.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970918.0193 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-18 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> 15th National Party Congress Closes (4) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
After the congress completed all its agenda, Jiang Zemin
delivered a speech to warm applause.
</P>
<P>
He said the current congress is of historic significance. It
approved the report of the 14th Central Committee, summed up the
experience and prepared for the future from a perspective of
historical development at the turn of the century, drew up a
cross-century blueprint for China's reform, opening-up and the
socialist modernization drive and put forward guiding principles
and policies on major domestic and international issues, Jiang
said.
</P>
<P>
The report is the crystalization of collective wisdom and
serves as the Party's political declaration and program of
action for the new century, he added.
</P>
<P>
The congress unanimously agreed with the establishment of Deng
Xiaoping Theory, which inherits and develops Mao Zedong Thought,
as the guiding ideology of the Party by stipulating it in the
Constitution of the CPC, he said.
</P>
<P>
It will guide all Party members and people of all nationalities
in China to achieve socialist modernization in the course of reforms
and opening-up, he said.
</P>
<P>
The new Central Committee elected by the current National
Congress proves that the Party has marched a step forward in
making the central collective leadership more revolutionized,
younger, better educated and professionally more competent, Jiang
said.
</P>
<P>
It is to greatly inspire all Party members and people of all
nationalities to hold high the great banner of Deng Xiaoping
Theory and push forward, with full confidence, the great cause of
socialism with Chinese characteristics into the 21st century, he
said.
</P>
<P>
After the election, Vice-President Rong Yiren, vice-chairmen of
the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress with no
party affiliation, vice-chairmen of the National Committee of the
Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference with no party
affiliation, leading officials of the non-communist parties and of
the All-China Federation of Industry and Commerce and public
personage without party affiliation were present as guests on the
rostrum.
</P>
<P>
Also present were leading Party officials from relevant
government departments.
</P>
<P>
The closing session ended at 1:15 p.m. to the tune of
"Internationale." 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
