and Armenia late last month is not directed against Azerbaijan.
</P>
<P>
The treaty will never be used to violate the territorial
integrity of Azerbaijan, Primakov said in a statement carried by
local media.
</P>
<P>
Russia is upset over the fact that some people in
Nagorno-Karabakh want to resort to force to solve the nine-year
conflict between Armenia and Azerbaijan over the disputed enclave,
the statement said.
</P>
