still unclear when we will be able to start producing the AN-70
here in Kiev," Antonov Design Bureau Director Petro Balabuyev was
quoted as saying at a press conference. (Ukraine-AN-70 Plane)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
SEOUL -- South Korean President Kim Young-sam is likely to give
special pardon to jailed former presidents Chun Doo-hwan and Roh
Tae-woo before the December presidential election, a high-ranking
government official said Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Kim has maintained a position of pardoning Chun and Roh at an
appropriate time after the election, but it is highly likely that
he will grant the amnesty before the presidential election as a
result of Kyonggi Governor Rhee In-je's entry into the race last
week, the official told reporters. (S.Korea-Presidential Amnesty)
</P>
