<HEADLINE> Fixture of European Cup Winners' Cup Soccer </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, September 17 (Xinhua) -- Following are the fixtures of
the European Cup Winners' Cup soccer tournament to be played on
Thursday (home team first):
</P>
<P>
First round first leg:
