<HEADLINE> Party Congress to Close This Morning </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 18 (Xinhua) -- The 15th National Congress of
the Communist Party of China (CPC), which opened on the 12th of this
month, will close here this morning.
</P>
<P>
AT today's closing session, the delegates to the congress will
elect the 15th CPC Central Committee and the new Central
Commission for Discipline Inspection (CCDI).
</P>
<P>
The session will also adopt resolutions on the report of the
14th Central Committee, the work report of the CCDI and the
"Amendment to the Constitution of the Communist Party of China."
</P>
</TEXT>
