member of the European Parliament, while the left wing Labor Party
chose an anti-nuclear campaigner Adi Roche as its candidate.
</P>
<P>
Well-known Irish singer Dana, whose real name is Rosemary
Scallon, has been unexpectedly nominated by municipal councilors
in four regions of the strongly Catholic republic.
</P>
<P>
Mary Robinson, who resigned her presidency last Friday, has
become United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights. 
