<HEADLINE> US to Send Experts to DPRK for Food Assessment </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, September 17 (Xinhua) -- The United States is
planning to send a team of experts to the Democratic People's
Republic of Korea (DPRK) to assess the food situation, the State
Department said today.
</P>
<P>
"This would be the first team of this nature sent by the United
States government," spokesman James Rubin told reporters.
</P>
<P>
