DPRK Tuesday during a meeting in New York and DPRK officials
welcomed the offer.
</P>
<P>
The U.S.-DPRK meeting was held in advance of the second round
of the preliminary session of four-party talks, which include the
DPRK, South Korea, the United States and China. The preliminary
session will begin Thursday at Columbia University in New York.
